Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: printed first
des:
Printed First, is an interesting way to test your knowledge of when certain words were first introduced.

There are three skill levels available. For those just getting started, there is the EASY mode.

If you find that too simple for you, there is the regular or normal mode. Try it. You will find this to be very challenging!

For those who find 'regular' is still not challenging enough, we have DIFFICULT mode! 
If you can master it, you are extremely proficient in your knowledge of words and when they were first used. 

You are a true scholar!

To start the skill, just say:

"Alexa, open Printed First"
"Alexa, start Printed First"
"Alexa, launch Printed First"

Please leave a review if you like this skill and find it challenging, or send us an email with your suggestions to: freeinfo@freeacademy.com. 

Your reviews encourage us to update our skills and to keep making more great skills, thanks!
